{"type":"text","timestamp":1775882688088,"sessionID":"ses_285266287ffelBHtLlbM2M7vsN","part":{"id":"prt_d7adb488d001pZOGFFJMGN9mNa","messageID":"msg_d7adb4040001Slqbm1LUQg3ALT","sessionID":"ses_285266287ffelBHtLlbM2M7vsN","type":"text","text":"Written `proposal.md` for AR-036 — Dify 插件集成. The proposal covers:\n\n- **Purpose**: Dify plugin integration for AgentCube Code Interpreter + PCAP Analyzer example app\n- **Scope**: Dify plugin files (manifest, provider, tool), PCAP Analyzer (FastAPI + LangGraph), containerization (Dockerfile + K8s)\n- **Impact**: New `integrations/dify-plugin/` and `example/pcap-analyzer/` directories, depends on `dify-plugin` and `agentcube-sdk`\n- **Alternatives**: Evaluated 5 options (plugin vs API gateway, single vs multi-tool, sync vs async, LangGraph vs pure code, uv vs pip)\n- **Implementation**: Directory structure, parameter schema, tool execution flow, PCAP analysis architecture\n- **Acceptance Criteria**: Plugin bootstrap, manifest compliance, tool invocation, PCAP endpoint, container/deployment config","time":{"start":1775882688085,"end":1775882688085}}}
